<tr>
<td>1970</td>
<td>Prix <a href="/wiki/Jean_XXIII" title="Jean XXIII"><span class="nowrap">Jean&#160;<abbr class="abbr" title="23"><span class="romain" style="text-transform:uppercase">XXIII</span></abbr></span></a></td>
