ica</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.universalis.fr/encyclopedie/mere-teresa/"><i>Encyclopædia Universalis</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/teresa-di-calcutta-santa"><i>Encyclopédie Treccani</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.enciclopedia.cat/EC-GEC-0065628.xml"><i>Gran Enciclopèdia Catalana</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=60933"><i>Hrvatska Enciklopedija</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/fr/article/mother-teresa"><i>L'Encyclopédie canadienne</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ne.se/uppslagsverk/encyklopedi/lång/moder-teresa"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.munzinger.de/search/go/document.jsp?id=00000015582">Munzinger Archiv</a></li></ul>
